edu.umd.cs.psl.parser

Interface PSLVisitor<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The return type of the visit operation. Use Void for operations with no return type.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PSLBaseVisitor, PSLModelLoader

    public interface PSLVisitor<T>
    This interface defines a complete generic visitor for a parse tree produced by PSLParser.
